room_title: Escape room "Mr. Boddy's Game Room" by Vizzini's House of Escapes in Salt Lake City
review: This was a really fun room to go too, iit was lots of fun and nice having so many rooms not just one or two, I definitely recommend it

room_title: Escape room "Mr. Boddy's Game Room" by Vizzini's House of Escapes in Salt Lake City
review: This place is AWESOME! Definitely the best escape room out there. It is very well put together and it's amazing how everything fit together so perfect! I would recommend this place to everyone!
